# 7Ô∏è‚É£ Commit & Push

![Image](https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/assets/images/git-commit-push-3e3acc438be0b1b47c7a4540f5cca854.png)

![Image](https://docs.databricks.com/aws/en/assets/images/git-folder-ui1-1314c0b409b264609ca019dc28e81d54.png)

![Image](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/databricks/_static/images/repos/git-commit-push.png)

Steps:

1. Click **Commit & Push**
2. Add message:

   ```
   Initial Bronze Layer Notebook
   ```
3. Click Commit & Push

Now code goes to GitHub.

